/* ==UserStyle==
@name           YouTube Studio Dark Theme
@namespace      USO Archive
@author         Lexan
@description    `This theme is an edit of a Dark Mode theme made by Leon Flame, please be sure to check out their theme here: https://userstyles.org/styles/185017/youtube-studio-vidiq-darkIf you would like to check out my channel, it can be found here: https://www.youtube.com/daniel55555d`
@version        202121.22.56
